<h2>Editing the Term</h2>
The term page lists the start and end dates for every marking period (for every track, if your school is multitrack) during the term. It also lists the number of classes in a typical school day (*or the maximum number of classes/teacher if your school does not have a consistent daily schedule) as well as the grades every teacher has the responsibility to collect ("Reported Grades", eg 'Semester', 'Final Exam', 'Cumulative', and all the marking period grades). From the term page, there are links to edit any aspect of the term - change the dates for any of the marking periods, add or remove marking periods, add, remove, or rename reported grades.</p>
